OAuthClient - Interface in com.simplegeo.client.http
An interface that defines the only method of the OAuth clients that is used outside of the response handler; the method that specifies the key & secret.
OAuthHttpClient - Class in com.simplegeo.client.http
A subclass of DefaultHttpClient that signs requests using a given OAuth key and secret.
